//
// WHY THIS FILE HAS NO PRISMA SYNTAX
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Previous versions of this stub contained a `datasource db` block (but no
// `generator` block). That was not enough: the Prisma CLI can still execute
// `prisma db push`, `prisma validate`, and `prisma migrate status` against a
// datasource-only schema, creating a silent footgun.
//
// This file now contains zero valid Prisma syntax:
//   • No datasource block  → prisma CLI cannot connect to any database
//   • No generator block   → prisma generate cannot run
//   • No model definitions → no schema drift possible
//
// The Prisma VS Code extension still finds the file (satisfying its "schema
// not found" check) but treats it as an empty schema — no false errors shown.
//
// CORRECT COMMANDS (all must be run from the monorepo root):
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//
//   npm run db:generate          # prisma generate --schema=packages/shared/...
//   npm run db:migrate           # prisma migrate dev --schema=packages/shared/...
//   npm run db:deploy            # prisma migrate deploy --schema=packages/shared/...
//   npm run db:studio            # prisma studio --schema=packages/shared/...
//   npm run db:push              # prisma db push --schema=packages/shared/...
//
//   OR with explicit --schema flag:
//
//   prisma generate  --schema=packages/shared/prisma/schema.prisma
//   prisma migrate dev --schema=packages/shared/prisma/schema.prisma
//   prisma migrate deploy --schema=packages/shared/prisma/schema.prisma
//   prisma db push   --schema=packages/shared/prisma/schema.prisma
//   prisma studio    --schema=packages/shared/prisma/schema.prisma
//
// WRONG (will fail or produce no output):
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//
//   prisma generate                        ← no datasource → fails
//   prisma migrate dev                     ← no datasource → fails
//   prisma generate --schema=apps/arkiol-core/prisma/schema.prisma  ← this file → fails
//
// BUILD SCRIPTS (already correct — do not change):
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//
//   apps/arkiol-core/package.json  "build":
//     prisma generate --schema=../../packages/shared/prisma/schema.prisma && next build
//
//   apps/arkiol-core/vercel.json   "buildCommand":
//     prisma generate --schema=../../packages/shared/prisma/schema.prisma && next build
